{"tid":938260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨：知道政府能容忍沒有能力的人","createTime":"2018-12-12T07:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T08:01:03.000Z","uid":75969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2c381059764de6ab47347da520e62c02c8c5aa","tid":938260,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181212/large/1544589448_acda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181212%2Flarge%2F1544589448_acda.png&h=8d585d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙中綫聆訊踏入第33日，港鐵主席馬時亨以港鐵最後一位證人的身份現身作供。曾發表知名金句「我哋話畀你聽OK就得啦」的馬時亨，今日在庭上回應本年6月15日港鐵向政府提交報告時資料出錯等事件，他坦言當時感到「震驚」及「失望」，又稱政府能容忍沒有能力的人，但不能容忍不準確的報告。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨指，自己作為港鐵非執行主席，職責上有局限，沒參與處理工程項目。他憶述今年5月底傳媒揭發剪鋼筋醜聞，時任港鐵工程總監黃唯銘認為報道失實，所以邀請傳媒到工地展示實際情況。他指，當時感到港鐵給予公眾缺乏透明度的觀感，港鐵亦承受極大壓力；而禮頓作為實際施工的公司，港鐵是禮頓僱主，曾要求禮頓向公眾交代但不果，批評禮頓不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n馬又強調，曾看過6月15日的報告，當日特別向沙中綫土木工程（南北線）前總經理胡宏利查詢報告提及的2.35萬個螺絲帽數量是否有文件支持，胡當時回應稱「有」。馬曾要求查看證明文件，但胡指涉及大量文件，而且放在地盤，故只交給他一張有不少簽名的試算表，當中有提及關鍵檢查點（hold point），他遂相信同事。其後馬於7月底出國回港，得悉工程團隊曾更改圖則設計，令呈報的螺絲帽數量出錯，他坦言感震驚和失望，當時亦收到3名政府官員的短訊，指事件是一場危機。<br />\n<br />\n其後，馬在8月初與特首林鄭月娥、運輸及房屋局局長陳帆等人開會，政府告知已對港鐵管理層失去信心，點名要求高層黃唯銘、李子文、胡宏利及黃智聰離職。馬指自己曾在政府工作6年，知道政府能容忍沒有能力的人，但不能容忍報告不準確，其後董事局會議一致接納政府意見，要求4人離職。<br />\n<br />\n中科代表大律師陶榮向馬時亨提出質疑，指港鐵提交給政府的報告沒有納入中科供詞，有違馬作為主席、推動開明文化和良好管治的目標，馬則指當日曾向港鐵人員查詢，但同事指有關內容涉貪污指控，亦可能構成誹謗，故沒有納入港鐵報告，他認為做法合理，亦有即時查詢有否向廉署舉報。<br />\n<br />\n馬稱港鐵轄下的工程委員會日後除了會檢視工程開支，亦會關注工程質量。他形容今次事件「是一個慘痛的教訓」，未來要向前看，「因為港鐵仍在未來40年、400年服務香港」，他作供後未有回應傳媒提問便離開。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181212/59020844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59020844&d=3LHRZsUT7ChIVUMdJzdIt7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=05ac27e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59020844&h=13cda1ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181212/59020844</a>"},{"pid":"ebeb4fb0b03266a4860ef4b772f5eba51b316293","tid":938260,"uid":75969,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SvCsKJt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSvCsKJt.png&h=4c994a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab5d6f3ed1224687efae745fbd617281fd20bb7","tid":938260,"uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"沒有能力的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87eb620d0f75c294154a28b896f2a7943ad63552","tid":938260,"uid":77196,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"知你冇撚用喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3e5a4820015651fdd9eae4c0ff53af1d21d5fa","tid":938260,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沒有能__的人&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>"},{"pid":"74e6ce29db563cd46ef65bd82051726c07b353cd","tid":938260,"uid":81273,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"地圖炮+回力標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86f40d017d34bf372613d924fb2a34cccb0541c","tid":938260,"uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"政府能容忍沒有能力的人，但不能容忍不準確的報告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒有能力的人=特首/司局長<br />\n<br />\n交報告的人=中下層人員，尤其技術人員"},{"pid":"2223052cd2cd6c3a6d5f6a947f8f0530f6860d22","tid":938260,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"偽造文件 炒魷就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab66dc3ed5533bcf63032cd82007d336598491ca","tid":938260,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"講佢自己?"},{"pid":"512dbac64ca7e9a355ebe372e11591d6203e8ed4","tid":938260,"uid":163302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"唔係幫佢講說話<br />\n馬生做官個陣已經算比較正常個位<br />\n佢應該係話緊整體政府入面好多冗員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce4ed45a12bdeb1bd7c51359f3edd5826e1b318","tid":938260,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係幫佢講說話<br />\n馬生做官個陣已經算比較正常個位<br />\n佢應該係話緊整體政府入面好多冗員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢個份狗糧係政府係鳩鐵，咁多年算擦鞋奶共狗定冗員？？？</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26ed02046bd4e57940682d5e5f743200334471a","tid":938260,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4152b9b7a91464afc5ae8ce8ecac3264a0290c85","tid":938260,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"唔怪得成個港共政府咁廢喇屌"},{"pid":"a87c3f08cfeb958c2ea90f2fe498054ad68254fc","tid":938260,"uid":128369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"佢咪其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}